Class TelloJavaToPython

  • java.lang.Object
    • TelloJavaToPython

  • public class TelloJavaToPython
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for communnicating between java and python with the intent of controlling a DJI Tello Drone All methods are public and static 9/30/2019 v1.0
    Author:
    MasterControlProgram: Seth Lewis
